# Process context routing

`all-*.md` files under `process/` are **routers**, not full knowledge.

Before proposing operational steps:

1. Read [process/context/all-context.md](../../process/context/all-context.md) (or the project copy after `vc-setup`).
2. Follow its routing table to the relevant deeper doc(s).
3. For tests, start at [process/context/tests/all-tests.md](../../process/context/tests/all-tests.md).

Do not read only the router and skip deeper docs — that produces stale or incomplete procedures.

When editing harness or protocol files, run `vc-audit-vc` / `vc-audit-context` after structural changes.
